- **`parseCDATA` function**: Parses the CDATA section and returns the end position.
- **`findEndTag` function**: Finds the end tag position.
- **`findEndTagCode` function**: Inner function to find the end tag based on the current tag.
- **`validateTagName` function**: Validates that tag names are properly formatted.

This solution ensures that all the rules provided are adhered to while parsing and validating the code snippet.

